Maintainer: Chang Hoon Han <paul9567@yuhs.ac>
Description: A package for the CHAPTER study. This package instantiates
    cohorts and computes incidence and basic cohort characteristics for
    multiple acute and chronic conditions using an ATLAS-compatible
    OHDSI stack (DatabaseConnector, SqlRender, CohortGenerator, etc.).
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
